      Title:
        m_Untranslated: Getting a Mouse Ray -Getting the World-Space Point
      Text:
        m_Untranslated: Now to convert this into <b>world-space</b> so we can do
          something useful with the information about where we just clicked. To do
          this we make use of <doc>Camera.ScreenPointToRay</doc>
      m_PollItems: []
